    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "# LEAD INTAKE & AI SCORING\n### A new lead submits the FlowBridge form (Name, Email, Phone and Request are required, Company Name is optional). An AI agent reads the free text Request and classifies the lead as Hot, Warm or Cold based on intent, seriousness, budget hints, urgency and the size of the opportunity.\n### It also returns a short reason for the score and writes a personalized reply tailored to what the lead actually asked for.",
        "height": 672,
        "width": 640
      },
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        -96,
        -304
      ],
      "id": "1010f366-2659-43fb-ac77-4263f5e1ab9b",
      "name": "Sticky Note"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## PARSE & AUTO REPLY\n### A Code node parses the AI output (priority, reason and reply) into clean fields the workflow can use. The personalized reply is then emailed to the lead automatically, so every lead gets a fast, relevant response.",
        "height": 672,
        "width": 400,
        "color": 2
      },
