        "content": "## ENRICH, ALERT & LOG\n### Hot leads trigger an instant email alert to the B2B sales team so they can act immediately. Each lead is enriched with a More Info field (simulated here for the demo, in production this would call a company lookup or enrichment API) and then logged to a Google Sheet with all its fields, its priority, the reason, and a status, as the single source of truth.",
